Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——op——
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.40,0:01:33.74,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,練字
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.28,0:01:43.12,Takagisan-huamian,,0,0,0,,{\fs70\frx2\fry349\frz359.9\pos(1580.8,377.2)}愛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.28,0:01:43.12,Takagisan-huamian,,0,0,0,,{\fs0\frx2\fry349\frz359.9\pos(1616.4,485.6)}與
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.28,0:01:43.12,Takagisan-huamian,,0,0,0,,{\fs70\frz2.121\frx2\fry349\pos(1496,508.4)}氣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.28,0:01:43.12,Takagisan-huamian,,0,0,0,,{\fs70\frz2.121\frx2\fry349\pos(1489.6,393.2)}勇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.28,0:01:43.12,Takagisan-huamian,,0,0,0,,{\frz2.121\frx2\fry349\pos(550,440)}努
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.28,0:01:43.12,Takagisan-huamian,,0,0,0,,{\frz2.121\frx2\fry349\pos(552,512)}力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.57,0:01:37.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.28,0:01:43.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那麼 大家寫一句自己喜歡的句子 下課時交上來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.13,0:01:52.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你在糾結呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.88,0:01:56.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學已經想好要寫甚麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.55,0:01:59.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒 我也沒有頭緒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.05,0:02:04.22,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,對了 我們來相互寫想讓對方做的事情怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.56,0:02:07.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,相互？想讓對方做的事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.64,0:02:08.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.40,0:02:13.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.40,0:02:20.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我想讓高木同學做的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.53,0:02:24.45,Takagisan-text1,,0,0,0,,{\fs150\fad(950,0)\frz345.6\frx14\fry336\pos(510,826)}禁\N止
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.53,0:02:24.45,Takagisan-text1,,0,0,0,,{\fs150\fad(950,0)\frz355.1\frx4\fry352\pos(1391.2,691.2)}捉\N弄\N人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.24,0:02:24.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.54,0:02:27.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,把「不要再捉弄我了」這一信息…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.08,0:02:33.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 感覺這樣做衹會起反作用
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.05,0:02:37.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,肯定會被高木同學拿來取樂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.59,0:02:41.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要在不挑釁高木同學的前提讓她反省的句子…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.47,0:02:45.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這可不簡單啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.73,0:02:51.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片 寫好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.81,0:02:53.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.77,0:02:55.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那麼交換看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.15,0:02:58.32,Takagisan-text1,,0,0,0,,{\fs120\an7}維持現状
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.07,0:03:01.03,Takagisan-text1,,0,0,0,,{\an4}忍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.07,0:03:01.03,Takagisan-text1,,0,0,0,,{\an4}耐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.20,0:03:00.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.57,0:03:03.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,「忍耐」?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.79,0:03:07.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.20,0:03:08.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,忍耐甚麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.16,0:03:10.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這是想讓我做的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.67,0:03:13.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 這個嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.17,0:03:14.80,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,説來話長
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.17,0:03:16.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,她沒理解
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.55,0:03:20.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是 説的太明白又會起反作用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.47,0:03:23.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真棘手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.93,0:03:27.85,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你寫了甚麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.02,0:03:29.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,「維持現狀」是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.73,0:03:32.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.52,0:03:33.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.61,0:03:38.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,希望西片能保持現在這樣容易捉弄的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.28,0:03:41.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學這傢伙 向我進攻了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.07,0:03:45.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,原來如此 原來是這種較量嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.45,0:03:47.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我現在可算是搞明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.04,0:03:50.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,咱們再來一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.50,0:03:52.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.34,0:03:57.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,給我走着瞧 高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.09,0:03:59.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今次輪到我進攻了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.59,0:04:03.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}你寫好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.30,0:04:04.22,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}還沒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.68,0:04:15.40,Takagisan-text1,,0,0,0,,{\frx0\fry12\move(1601.6,1210.8,1576.2,749)}柔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.68,0:04:15.40,Takagisan-text1,,0,0,0,,{\frx12\fry10\move(1564.8,746.8,1558.4,270)}温
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.93,0:04:15.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就這樣 讓高木同學知道她不夠温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.65,0:04:18.53,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學 等着受打擊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.40,0:04:21.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.86,0:04:24.74,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學在煩惱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.03,0:04:29.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我覺得這都是因為高木同學不夠温柔哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.79,0:04:34.42,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我剛剛才發現 西片的字寫得不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.96,0:04:36.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不如説 寫得很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.75,0:04:38.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你有在哪裏學過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.55,0:04:40.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 沒有啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.72,0:04:45.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我很喜歡西片寫的字
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.65,0:04:59.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,給你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.65,0:05:02.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,謝謝…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.03,0:05:07.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,咦 怎麼好像突然温柔起來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.28,0:05:09.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這究竟是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.62,0:05:13.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,難道説 衹是我沒有注意到而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.62,0:05:16.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學其實很温柔嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.75,0:05:20.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 這不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.67,0:05:26.22,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片 不要動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.81,0:05:36.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你臉上沾到東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.73,0:05:40.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好 我想到好點子了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.75,0:05:59.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.13,0:06:02.34,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那麼從西片開始揭曉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.38,0:06:04.42,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,誒 不是同時嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.76,0:06:06.88,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你就別管了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.80,0:06:09.76,Takagisan-text1,,0,0,0,,{\fs120\an4}不\N許\N再
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.80,0:06:09.76,Takagisan-text1,,0,0,0,,{\fs120\an4}捉\N弄\N我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.14,0:06:14.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,最後還是重寫了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.68,0:06:17.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你的字果然寫得很有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.69,0:06:19.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,甚麼 你的關注點是那裏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.69,0:06:23.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,總之 不要再捉弄我了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.40,0:06:24.53,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,誒 不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.11,0:06:26.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你回答得太乾脆了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.16,0:06:29.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,知道了知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.70,0:06:31.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,儘量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.87,0:06:33.74,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那麼 高木同學的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.24,0:06:35.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.29,0:06:37.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我的是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.17,0:06:39.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.38,0:06:44.38,Takagisan-text1,,0,0,0,,{\fs120\pos(1402,632)}你\N臉\N上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.38,0:06:44.38,Takagisan-text1,,0,0,0,,{\fs120\pos(800,918)}沾\N了\N墨\N汁\N哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.27,0:06:58.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是那時…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.35,0:07:02.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,明明剛才還在説儘量做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.65,0:07:05.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因為 在説之前我就做了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.95,0:07:21.75,Takagisan-text1,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,1300)\fs100\pos(256,524)}不\N要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.95,0:07:21.75,Takagisan-text1,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,1300)\fs100\pos(172,524)}大\N意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.95,0:07:21.75,Takagisan-text2,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,1300)\fs100\pos(1168,580)}不\N要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.95,0:07:21.75,Takagisan-text2,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,1300)\fs100\pos(1070,576)}大\N意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.42,0:07:27.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,換裝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.68,0:07:34.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.72,0:07:35.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.89,0:07:39.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是時候該換短袖了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.19,0:07:41.85,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.06,0:07:47.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,也吿訴早苗明天開始穿短袖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.78,0:07:49.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.53,0:07:52.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你們在「是」甚麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.33,0:07:57.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.29,0:08:05.34,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你們倆不熱嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.51,0:08:12.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.26,0:08:17.22,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不是約好了要一起換裝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.10,0:08:19.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,有這回事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.52,0:08:21.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,有的 你搶跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.02,0:08:26.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.36,0:08:31.11,Takagisan-subtitle,,0,0,0,,{\fad(900,0)\fs150\blur2\pos(1412,504)}第二天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.41,0:08:37.53,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,短袖果然很涼快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.78,0:08:39.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.87,0:08:43.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你們在「是」甚麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.04,0:08:45.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 早苗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.04,0:08:48.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,早上…好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.72,0:08:58.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不是説要大家一起換嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.69,0:09:06.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我忘記説了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.44,0:09:12.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,疼疼疼疼疼…快放開我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.53,0:09:18.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,英譯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.62,0:09:20.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,That'right
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.99,0:09:24.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,Walk down this street to the post office
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.33,0:09:26.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,and turn left there
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.25,0:09:28.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,You will see the station
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.46,0:09:30.80,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,It takes five minute from here
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.71,0:09:35.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天我一定要戰勝高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.05,0:09:38.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,有甚麼好方法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.35,0:09:43.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好久沒弄過嚇人盒子了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.18,0:09:45.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是沒有材料
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.60,0:09:48.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,現在開始做怕是來不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.94,0:09:52.53,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那麼 這一段…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.28,0:09:54.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.45,0:09:56.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.86,0:10:00.87,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,別「是」了 給我快點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.54,0:10:06.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,16
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.08,0:10:09.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是16
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.50,0:10:16.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這節不是數學課 是英語課 英語課
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.17,0:10:17.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我讓你翻譯這一段
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.51,0:10:19.85,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.14,0:10:21.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,夠了 坐下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.02,0:10:27.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我都吿訴你是第16頁了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.15,0:10:31.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你是故意讓我誤解的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.06,0:10:33.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒想到你真的誤解了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.19,0:10:35.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,果然是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.32,0:10:39.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你在想甚麼東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.20,0:10:41.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.33,0:10:43.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你在想甚麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.00,0:10:49.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒甚麼 不是甚麼大事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.13,0:10:53.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.17,0:10:58.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你是不是在想甚麼下流的東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.72,0:11:00.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,甚麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.76,0:11:02.22,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,才沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.47,0:11:03.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.60,0:11:04.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真的沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.31,0:11:07.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,絕對沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.68,0:11:08.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.64,0:11:13.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,其實是在想怎麼樣才能報復我平時的所作所為吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.48,0:11:18.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,誰知道呢…究竟是甚麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.45,0:11:19.74,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,被我説中了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.95,0:11:23.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因為你一直很在意我 我就在想是不是這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.53,0:11:26.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不要明知故問嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.25,0:11:30.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因為看西片的反應很有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.83,0:11:33.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,然後呢 想到甚麼好主意沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.34,0:11:39.09,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,當然 想到了絕佳的主意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.42,0:11:42.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,肯定能奏效的主意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.31,0:11:47.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是真的就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.10,0:11:49.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,她一點也不怕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.98,0:11:52.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,難道她看穿了我甚麼也沒想出來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.11,0:11:55.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,然後呢 是甚麼主意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.73,0:11:58.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,説出來不就沒用了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.19,0:11:59.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,給我個提示也好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.78,0:12:00.74,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.82,0:12:02.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,比起這個 要好好聽課…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.87,0:12:06.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天是18號
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.66,0:12:09.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學的學號也是18號
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.00,0:12:12.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是能讓高木同學分心不聽課
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.46,0:12:15.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,讓她被點到時不知所措被老師臭罵一頓…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.55,0:12:17.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.84,0:12:18.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,甚麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.88,0:12:21.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天早上你吃了甚麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.80,0:12:24.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,吃了山藥飯 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.30,0:12:27.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒甚麼 我就問問…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.68,0:12:32.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你喜歡山藥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.81,0:12:34.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯 挺喜歡的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.69,0:12:37.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,早上吃了的話 感覺一整天都會很精神
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.61,0:12:39.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊 我也有同感
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.44,0:12:41.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.07,0:12:44.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我嗎 我的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.37,0:12:46.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你猜猜看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.08,0:12:50.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我想想 是米飯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.66,0:12:52.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,米飯算甚麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.71,0:12:55.42,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,甚麼 我以為你不喜歡吃麪包
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.79,0:12:56.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.67,0:12:58.80,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 雖然我喜歡吃米飯…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.96,0:13:02.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,很好 她的注意力轉移到課堂以外了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.76,0:13:04.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學也是米飯派嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.93,0:13:07.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那我點人從頭開始讀下一頁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.72,0:13:10.22,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天是18號
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.72,0:13:11.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.60,0:13:13.85,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.06,0:13:19.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣 這下你不知道了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.40,0:13:23.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,I'll not do such a thing
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.32,0:13:25.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好 正確
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.99,0:13:27.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,甚麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.41,0:13:32.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.25,0:13:35.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你 你在説甚麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.37,0:13:38.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可惡 還真有一手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.17,0:13:39.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不愧是高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.75,0:13:41.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,得想想下一招了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.05,0:13:45.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,果然還是要用嚇人盒子直接進攻…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.72,0:13:49.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 我不是沒材料嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.64,0:13:53.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片 你在煩惱甚麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.06,0:13:56.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 沒甚麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.69,0:14:00.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你又在想我的事情了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.94,0:14:05.74,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這種説法有點不太對…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.49,0:14:08.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,而且我才沒有想呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.53,0:14:09.87,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.20,0:14:12.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那果然是下流的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.79,0:14:13.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,都説不是了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.13,0:14:21.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我衹想着西片的事情哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.96,0:14:24.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,甚麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.09,0:14:27.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊哈 你臉紅了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.59,0:14:30.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,才沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.26,0:14:31.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.01,0:14:35.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,反正也是像現在這樣 想着要怎麼捉弄我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.36,0:14:45.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.74,0:14:50.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,剛剛那個停頓 搞甚麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.99,0:14:53.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那麼下一個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.58,0:14:57.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因為是6月18號 加起來是24號
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.29,0:14:57.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.08,0:15:00.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,甚麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.46,0:15:03.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.47,0:15:15.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,泳池開放的第一天竟然衹能在旁邊看着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.77,0:15:19.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是手沒有受傷的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.77,0:15:27.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真好啊 大家都很開心的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.86,0:15:28.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.99,0:15:33.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,泳池開放的第一天竟然衹能在旁邊看着 真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.91,0:15:36.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學也請假了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.66,0:15:37.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.54,0:15:41.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片是因為手上的傷口嗎 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.13,0:15:48.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嘛 一言難盡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.13,0:15:52.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是想摸野貓然後被咬了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.34,0:15:54.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,甚麼 你為甚麼會知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.47,0:15:56.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我明明沒吿訴過其他人的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.72,0:16:00.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 猜對了嗎 我明明衹是隨口説的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.73,0:16:02.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你真笨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.32,0:16:11.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學才是 為甚麼今天要請假…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.08,0:16:17.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,話説起來…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.37,0:16:21.87,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,女生在游泳課的時候請假往往是因為生理期
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.87,0:16:25.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,課本上説 生理期時肚子會作痛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.04,0:16:29.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,保健體育課之王高尾是這麼説的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.51,0:16:32.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 沒甚麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.26,0:16:36.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,還是算了 感覺這是不能碰的高壓綫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.06,0:16:40.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,想問我為甚麼今天要請假嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.93,0:16:42.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,被她聽見了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.52,0:16:46.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,既然我猜中了西片受傷的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.07,0:16:49.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那今次輪到西片來猜了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.82,0:16:54.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,身體不適
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.03,0:16:57.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這種模稜兩可的答案可不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.37,0:17:01.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,算了吧 我也不想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.16,0:17:04.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那算我贏了可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.54,0:17:10.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我知道了 我猜就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.67,0:17:12.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,衹能猜一次哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.17,0:17:14.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,雖然我覺得你肯定猜不到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.09,0:17:17.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這個高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.55,0:17:20.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,信心滿滿地認為我説不出生理期這三個字嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.68,0:17:23.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那你可就太小看我了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.48,0:17:25.85,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不對 她可是高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.81,0:17:27.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,也有可能是在給我下套
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.98,0:17:33.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是我鼓起勇氣回答是生理期的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.20,0:17:36.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,才不是呢 真沒禮貌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.45,0:17:40.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,完全有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.79,0:17:42.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不對 她可是高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.08,0:17:46.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,她肯定早就看穿我的想法了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.08,0:17:48.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,連我會猶豫不決的事情也…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.00,0:17:51.88,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,然後再預料我的對策
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.22,0:17:57.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你連女生在游泳課時請假的原因都不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.22,0:18:00.10,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那我贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.31,0:18:03.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,到底是陷阱還是真心話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.27,0:18:05.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,還是偽裝成真心話的陷阱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.27,0:18:07.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,還是裝作是陷阱其實是真心話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.61,0:18:10.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,越來越搞不懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.36,0:18:15.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可惡啊 剛才她那表情究竟是甚麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.74,0:18:18.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,其他的可能性呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.12,0:18:20.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,比如受傷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.54,0:18:25.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好像沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.29,0:18:30.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,看上去也不像是身體不適到無法運動的程度
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.00,0:18:34.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那麼 果然還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.09,0:18:35.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.68,0:18:43.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真好啊 大家都很開心的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.89,0:18:47.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我還要頂着酷暑絞盡腦汁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.31,0:18:49.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,和高木同學鬥智鬥勇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.77,0:18:53.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片你有好好在想嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.57,0:18:56.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,感覺你剛才開始一直看着在游泳的女生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.20,0:18:58.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,才沒有看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.82,0:19:00.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.82,0:19:04.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,都説男生衹知道盯着女生的胸部不放
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.79,0:19:07.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,都説了我沒看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.83,0:19:11.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.79,0:19:13.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,雖然這麼説有些對不起她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.71,0:19:15.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,胸有點平啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.71,0:19:22.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,據説胸小的女生會格外在意胸部的事情哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.60,0:19:24.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,喜歡提前把午飯吃掉的木村這樣説過
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.43,0:19:28.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,難道説 高木同學是因為對自己的胸部感到自卑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.35,0:19:30.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,才不去上游泳課的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.35,0:19:33.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你果然不知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.69,0:19:35.53,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天也是我贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.03,0:19:39.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學 我已經知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.61,0:19:43.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學在意自己胸部的大小吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.33,0:19:47.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這種話怎麼説得出口啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.58,0:19:49.87,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒禮貌也要有個限度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.46,0:19:53.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,到頭來能回答的選項衹有生理期而已嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.84,0:19:56.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是那個也挺沒禮貌的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.05,0:20:00.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你還在想嗎 差不多到時間了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.55,0:20:04.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒事 課本上也有這些內容 不是甚麼令人羞恥的話題
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.64,0:20:07.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒錯 堂堂正正地説出來就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.64,0:20:08.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.31,0:20:14.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學請假的原因是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.36,0:20:17.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,生理期
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.49,0:20:22.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,猜錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.37,0:20:25.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你在跟女孩子説甚麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.62,0:20:28.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 因為課本上也有寫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.41,0:20:29.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,再説 一般而言…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.96,0:20:34.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片 你臉紅到脖子根去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.46,0:20:41.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,所以答案是胸部的自卑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.05,0:20:44.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,太好笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.52,0:20:49.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,順帶一提
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.94,0:21:04.87,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因為胸部太小感到難為情也是錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.16,0:21:07.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.91,0:21:10.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我還是想去游泳 可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.70,0:21:11.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.08,0:21:15.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那她為甚麼要請假…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.75,0:21:19.80,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那麼 也欣賞到了西片有趣的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.96,0:21:21.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,去游一會兒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.59,0:21:25.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,難道説 你是為了捉弄我才請假的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.56,0:21:34.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,等手的傷好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.61,0:21:39.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我們一起去游泳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.78,0:21:50.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.58,0:21:56.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,別被她騙了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.58,0:22:00.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要真和她去游泳了 她又會想着要捉弄我了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.00,0:22:03.80,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學就是這樣的人
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——OPJP——
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.10,0:00:05.73,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)\an1}勘違いされちゃったっていいよ、君となら
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.81,0:00:10.11,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)\an1}なんて思ってたって言わないけどね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.15,0:00:20.45,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}近づく空の香りを隣で感じていたいの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.91,0:00:29.30,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}校庭で君のことを一番に見つけて今日は
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.34,0:00:37.55,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}なんて話しかけようか？ ちょっと考えるの楽しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.60,0:00:40.52,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}風に揺らされるカーテン
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.31,0:00:45.90,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}不意打ちに当たる日差し
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.98,0:00:49.82,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}眩しそうな顔を笑ったら
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.03,0:00:53.70,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}照れて伏せちゃうのね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.61,0:01:01.79,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}憂鬱なテストも吹き飛ばせるような
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.95,0:01:10.09,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}ねえ、二人で秘密の約束をしたいなって提案です
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.46,0:01:15.51,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}勘違いされちゃったっていいよ、君となら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.72,0:01:19.51,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}なんて思ってたって言わないけどね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.51,0:01:29.73,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}近づく空の香りを隣で感じていたいの
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——OPCH——
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.10,0:00:05.73,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)\an1}會錯意了也沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.81,0:00:10.11,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)\an1}和你一起就是幸福 這樣想著卻不告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.15,0:00:20.45,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}瀰漫在周圍的那陣幽香 想在你的身邊靜靜感受
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.91,0:00:29.30,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}在校園的庭院 第一個發現你的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.34,0:00:37.55,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}今天要和你說些什麼呢 即便是想著這些也是一種樂趣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.60,0:00:40.52,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}窗簾隨風起舞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.31,0:00:45.90,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}不經意地投入一束陽光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.98,0:00:49.82,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}你那美麗的容顏笑起來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.03,0:00:53.70,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}羞得我抬不起頭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.61,0:01:01.79,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}風兒喧囂 似要吹散考試的憂鬱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.95,0:01:10.09,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}吶 我想要和你一起 立下兩人的秘密約定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.46,0:01:15.51,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}會錯意了也沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.72,0:01:19.51,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}和你一起就是幸福 這樣想著卻不告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.51,0:01:29.73,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}瀰漫在周圍的那陣幽香 想在你的身邊靜靜感受
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——EDJP——
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.06,0:22:19.27,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}ロマンティック　恋のアンテナは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.65,0:22:24.99,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}嵐で　何処かへ飛んでいった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.99,0:22:29.49,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}噓でしょう　冷たくあしらった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.49,0:22:32.49,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}こしゃくなえくぼに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.49,0:22:36.50,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}ちょっと　心が揺れてる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.50,0:22:47.43,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}本当は本気であたしを叱ってくれる大事な人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.68,0:22:56.14,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}なんて 言いたらアイツは得意気になるから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.60,0:22:59.35,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}もう褒めたりしない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.52,0:23:04.82,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}退屈な運命に　飽き飽きしたね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.07,0:23:11.66,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}知らない言葉で　解き放して　ねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.66,0:23:17.12,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}ダーリン　ダーリン　心の　扉を壊してよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.12,0:23:22.92,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}大切のことは目を見て　言って
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.92,0:23:28.30,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}あなたとならば　この街を抜け出せる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.30,0:23:34.93,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}今すぐ連れ出して　My Sweet Sweet Darling
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——EDCH——
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.06,0:22:19.27,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}浪漫愛情的天線
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.65,0:22:24.99,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}狂風中不知飛向何方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.99,0:22:29.49,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}怎麼會這樣 對我這麼冷淡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.49,0:22:32.49,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}洋洋自得的酒窩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.49,0:22:36.50,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}稍微 有點心動
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.50,0:22:47.43,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}其實 你是重視我而認真批評我的人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.68,0:22:56.14,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}如果這樣說的話你一定會洋洋得意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.60,0:22:59.35,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}所以再也不會表揚你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.52,0:23:04.82,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}單調乏味的命運 我早已厭倦了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.07,0:23:11.66,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}用未知的言語 解放我 好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.66,0:23:17.12,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}Darling Darling 推倒封印心靈的大門吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.12,0:23:22.92,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}重要的事情就應該親眼見證 親口述說
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.92,0:23:28.30,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}只要和你在一起 就能闖出這座小鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.30,0:23:34.93,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}現在就帶我走吧 My Sweet Sweet Darling
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——STAFF——
